<p>I feel like this should be simple...</p>  <p>Say I have:</p>  <pre><code>$project = new Project(); $project-&gt;save();  $user = new User(); $user-&gt;save();  $user-&gt;projects()-&gt;save($project); </code></pre>  <p>This works fine. How can I remove the project from the user?</p>  <p>I would expect something like:</p>  <pre><code>$user = User::find('someUserID'); $project = Project::find('someProjectID'); $user-&gt;projects()-&gt;remove($project); </code></pre>  <p>And yet it's not that simple.</p>